hxCMS
Designed by: MrHeroux.com

Version: 7.1.3


System Requirements:

	PHP with pdo extention

	Configure php.ini
	memory_limit = 32M

	upload_max_filesize = 15M
	post_max_size = 20M
	
	Apache with mod_rewrite
	MySQL



Installation:

	1. Run sql in database
	
	2. Edit config.ini.php 
		
		Enter server and sudomain settings.
	
		Enter database settings.